Unique Order Numbers	Short readable orderId	Better UX, easy support
Idempotency	Prevent double charge/order	No accidental dup orders
Deadlock Handling	Transaction timeout, error logs	Avoid stuck orders
Logging	Per-event log with context	Debug, audit, analysis
Extra Validation	Cross-check DB for every entity	Data integrity, security
Restock on Cancel	Transactional cancel support	Inventory accuracy
Rate Limiting	API limit per-user	Bot/abuse 


